- pods are k8 objects that are basic unit for running containers inside k8 cluster.pod contains one or more containers
that shares same resource (storage, network resources, namespaces) with in pod.pods are ephemeral resources , that pods can be terminated and restart on another in k8 cluster at any point of time.  

```
    kubectl apply -f <pod.yaml>

    kubectl get pods

    <!-- full info of pod -->
    kubectl describe pod 

    kubectl delete pod <pod_name>

```